    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Foundations that sustain loads by distributing them over a large planar surface; may support one or more columns, piers, or walls.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
